{"metadata":null,"content":"\\documentclass{article}\n\\usepackage[utf8]{inputenc}\n\\usepackage[paperwidth=4in, \n    paperheight=6in,\n    left=0.50in,\n    right=0.50in,\n    top=0.50in,\n    bottom=0.50in]{geometry}\n\\usepackage{caption}\n\\usepackage{subcaption}\n\\usepackage{graphicx}\n\\usepackage{dblfloatfix}\n\\usepackage{setspace}\n\\doublespacing\n\\usepackage{moresize}\n\\pagestyle{empty}\n\\begin{document}\n\\sffamily\n\n{\\Large \\textbf{Thank you for your purchase!}} \\\\\n\\\\\nIf you have any comments, questions, or concerns related to your product, please send a message through eBay for support. \\\\\n\\\\\nYour feedback means a lot, so please let us know how your experience was!\n\\begin{figure*}[!b]\n\\centering\n\\begin{subfigure}{.5\\textwidth}\n  \\centering\n<py>\nimport qrcode\nimport os\n\ncwd = os.getcwd()\n\nimg = qrcode.make(\"https://aspentech.xyz\")\ntype(img)\nimg.save(os.path.join(cwd,\"weblink.png\"))\nprint(\"\\\\includegraphics[width=1.5in]{%s}\" % (os.path.join(cwd,\"weblink.png\")))\n</py>\n  \\caption{My Website}\n\\end{subfigure}%\n\\begin{subfigure}{.5\\textwidth}\n  \\centering\n<py>\n\nimg = qrcode.make(\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/aspentechemporium\")\ntype(img)\nimg.save(os.path.join(cwd,\"eblink.png\"))\nprint(\"\\\\includegraphics[width=1.5in]{%s}\" % (os.path.join(cwd,\"eblink.png\")))\n</py>\n  \\caption{My eBay}\n\\end{subfigure}\n\\end{figure*}\n\n\\end{document}","id":"20250319-1419-8439-8378-c5dd92888f9d"}